E '''Jermanikani chib''' (pe Jermanikani ''Deutsche Sprache'') si yek vestutni jermane, tay [[Indo-Ewropikane chhiba|Indo-Europikani chib]]. E Jermanikani chib si e [[daki chib]], a 100.000.000 jene. 
